extendedInfo.description: Mobile Banking from your Android!With the Mobile Community from Community Bank & Trust, you can bank anytime, anywhere right from your mobile phone. The Mobile Community offers you the ability to view account balances and recent transactions, transfer funds between your accounts and even pay your bills.  You can also find the nearest branch or ATM and be directly connected to Voice Banking. Requirements: If you have a checking or savings account with us, mobile banking is free. All you need is an SMS text message and/or internet enabled mobile device, and be a Community Bank & Trust Option Online user.Security: You can rest easy knowing that your transactions are secure as part of the Mobile Community.
